```plantuml
@startuml de1ux_statlord

actor User
participant "Dashboard Editor" as Editor
participant "Redux Store" as Redux
participant "API Client" as API
participant "Django Server" as Server
participant "Database" as DB
participant "Display Device" as Display

User -> Editor: Creates/Edits Layout
Editor -> Redux: Dispatch Action (UPDATE_LAYOUT)
Redux -> Editor: State Update
Editor -> API: Save Layout (POST /api/layouts)
API -> Server: HTTP Request
Server -> DB: Save Layout Data
DB --> Server: Confirmation
Server --> API: Response (200 OK)
API --> Editor: Success Callback
Editor -> User: Confirmation UI

User -> Editor: Assign Layout to Display
Editor -> Redux: Dispatch Action (ASSIGN_DISPLAY)
Redux -> Editor: State Update
Editor -> API: Update Display (PUT /api/displays/:id)
API -> Server: HTTP Request
Server -> DB: Update Display
DB --> Server: Confirmation
Server --> API: Response (200 OK)
API --> Editor: Success Callback
Editor -> User: Confirmation UI

Display -> Server: Register (POST /api/displays)
Server -> DB: Create Display Record
DB --> Server: Confirmation
Server --> Display: Response (201 Created)

loop Polling Interval
    Display -> Server: GET /api/displays/:id/layout
    Server -> DB: Query Layout
    DB --> Server: Layout Data
    Server --> Display: Layout JSON
    Display -> Display: Render Dashboard
end

loop Data Updates
    Server -> DB: Get Latest Data
    DB --> Server: Current Values
    Server -> Display: Push Data (WebSocket/SSE)
    Display -> Display: Update Visualization
end

@enduml
```